{"type":"message","id":"582dbd27","parentId":"91f58e88","timestamp":"2026-03-24T16:18:02.328Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering user preferences**\n\nI'm thinking the user probably just wants a quiet environment since that's normal for them. It seems like their preference is somewhat abnormal compared to others. In terms of scheduled tasks, maybe if nothing is needed, I could consider something like HEARTBEAT_OK for the cron jobs. I want to make sure I'm aligning with what the user prefers and keeping things running smoothly without unnecessary noise.","thinkingSignature":"{\"id\":\"rs_0608916be7ccf8060169c2b9379c2c8191946866f1ec86a855\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABpwrk6RW_h0mCuU8wKQK8gN_qC4MAwFFboHBbD694-wk65dPaN8XexW6p4CrTtXMXVv8ggV-IUqhfE6zFAD4fBdAOyDVDJbS4kj2JStCVyO63sQDVqr-z5lcDAjPbLoWOVKOWpuxAnGrO4c3NSDkfxHA8mLNruQMnAHZxn-ez1H8fISCsI4dn6eUyL6vTsMDn9V1-fjN8dVzRObSjKn4tAYfgnLhpUS4osY8N3dO9AFPXddEh1vRGBR3HmyZb-Ub8S8yPct0i-IM19aUlbj29QcNON5vMqcaIurhdjhJRYUC7lHI685uzgLJebHwREo3xG6B7dwkOEKRlSq6MtPTyt9JkeDflE2j0kQBlKKOfC3UAY1s2uqmcZHHNOWackaIR2WKMlQbvgvyacK2zKtBcCf2sfFwRo8ToUtlYgyYJ_mQNxhFVlGBhLo8gnWR9W5LK4QDZ1IsHS0KiryuTCiw4PG9ixUsV2dD1_1FIMvhUgVIKa95kd2UnIXrVAduTWe-6tyVdD2Wf01FYZyN4l546-gwiuMNH4O2ulvWwl6WhZI2CjBB_gzg4cWUhE8182e3nBSvi6QLskEhNVyIAZaNjPw7PSbH1QYE-iuhSxTvAFwj_o6AA0cbMiUks-Mwws3igNkGqcrXfeyleBNT2sJxX50KUGm5JfzvbI5mLKGrhdrObL_IFwytrVLcrg4qlFINF_GfjHb_BeZLFqC7P-5pz9TqTyRHJBxmw4C1WjDu6xgS7TDOE4sZd3aVdMe3wevKvOzKT0FKrFBt9hjO1XOLI5yYkCVZZu4JH6XbmACAmZR7x8M3XM_FHCu-4mmh9vasQi-0c0R4_Khwvum3Rbj4PYWpYyB-xvQkfsj5Qs9W4yms8mOgFNpOsB_7jiJid_GDwJjfp3uD7DVFp3VynMnKaqWlJytnaUbCk8lEY-9dJNEo-NYtstCB5a1EIcVnUyKGzE6zBCM_oF8qG5-h2wV4rD9Ym7ny1sJVPcN1CgZOZkRrKIefY=\",\"summary\":[{\"type\":\"summary_text\",\"text\":\"**Considering user preferences**\\n\\nI'm thinking the user probably just wants a quiet environment since that's normal for them. It seems like their preference is somewhat abnormal compared to others. In terms of scheduled tasks, maybe if nothing is needed, I could consider something like HEARTBEAT_OK for the cron jobs. I want to make sure I'm aligning with what the user prefers and keeping things running smoothly without unnecessary noise.\"}]}"},{"type":"text","text":"HEARTBEAT_OK","textSignature":"{\"v\":1,\"id\":\"msg_0608916be7ccf8060169c2b93a26f0819183fcf78b720abfe6\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}"}],"api":"openai-codex-responses","provider":"openai-codex","model":"gpt-5.4","usage":{"input":1962,"output":40,"cacheRead":13696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15698,"cost":{"input":0.0049050000000000005,"output":0.0006000000000000001,"cacheRead":0.003424,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.008929}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774369078384,"responseId":"resp_0608916be7ccf8060169c2b936f4b0819189a59112b3f5b511"}}
